Class LabelTransformer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tribuo.interop.tensorflow.LabelTransformer

    public class LabelTransformer
extends Object
implements OutputTransformer<Label>
    Can convert a Label into a Tensor containing a 32-bit integer and can convert a vector of 32-bit floats into a Prediction or a Label.
